They told us peace was something to earn,
something outsourced to cities, systems, and signatures. <img
    loading="lazy"
    class="chatlog__emoji "
    alt="🏙"
    title="🏙"
    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f3d9.svg">️<img
