I experienced unlawful restrictions on access to my own funds—without due process, transparency, or remedy.

This was not confined to one institution, jurisdiction, or border.
It revealed a coordinated hand operating beyond national boundaries, unconcerned with sovereignty or lawful limits.

Relying solely on centralized systems creates a single point of failure.
Self-custody and offline storage are lawful acts of resilience.

Decentralization isn’t rebellion.
It’s self-protection.

#FinancialSovereignty #SelfCustody #RuleOfLaw #Decentralization #Resilience #StaySovereign

