Society teaches us the box—boundaries, containment, ownership—and calls it achievement. But the box feeds ego, not spirit. God cannot be boxed; to try is only to wrap a lid around what we think we understand. In truth, we begin at the lid and journey into the well—the depths of life, faith, and experience—where meaning flows without end.

#ItsNotABox #TheWellIsTheJourney #PerspectiveShift #EgoVsSpirit #HiddenDepths #LookCloser #JourneyWithin

