In my NSW Family Court case, my eldest son’s ADHD medication was changed without my knowledge or consent. After that change, professionals engaged without my involvement described him as ‘distraught’ and ‘emotionless.’
I have documentation showing that before this medication, a different psychologist found no such issues — yet that report was ignored.
Based on this evidence, I believe this is not a mistake. This is a system acting with criminal intent. It doped my child to create a false narrative against his father.
People need to see how a ‘pay-to-win’ family law system can harm children to discredit a parent.

#FamilyCourt #NSW #InformedConsent #FathersRights #ChildSafety #PayToWin #SystemExposed #ADHD #JusticeForChildren #LegalReform #DelaneyRoberts #RelationSpace

