<div class=chatlog__message-group><div id=chatlog__message-container-1470085487543713874 class=chatlog__message-container data-message-id=1470085487543713874><div class=chatlog__message><div class=chatlog__message-aside><img class=chatlog__avatar src=https://cdn.discordapp.com/embed/avatars/4.png alt=Avatar loading=lazy></div><div class=chatlog__message-primary><div class=chatlog__header><span class=chatlog__author title=dadventuressteve data-user-id=1264035953933156432>Veilocity</span> <span class=chatlog__timestamp title="Sunday, 8 February 2026 7:54 PM"><a href=#chatlog__message-container-1470085487543713874>8/02/2026 7:54 PM</a></span></div><div class="chatlog__content chatlog__markdown"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve><strong>Protecting Innocence in the Digital Age <img
    loading="lazy"
    class="chatlog__emoji "
    alt="🕊"
    title="🕊"
    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f54a.svg">️ 10/09/2025 - Germany</strong>

The story of Eden was never just a myth—it was a warning.
In today’s world, the “apples” are everywhere: in schools, on screens, in the hands of peers. I’ve lived it—my sons once came home begging to access content like FNAF because their friends had already opened the door. In that moment, the enemy had already arrived.
If I say yes, I hand them over. If I say no, I become the villain. Either way, the peace is broken. Not at home—but back at school. That’s where the breach began.
<img
    loading="lazy"
    class="chatlog__emoji "
    alt="🍎"
    title="apple"
    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f34e.svg"> We don’t need just laws—we need spiritual firewalls. Because peace must belong to us, not be forced on us. The second peace is imposed, it becomes control.
Those of us who’ve awakened—we know. We’ve gone within. We’ve met God in the silence. We’ve stopped reaching for smoke, drink, or noise to fill the void.
We protect the garden not through war—but through wisdom. Not by closing eyes—but by opening hearts.

#SpiritualAwakening #ProtectTheChildren #TreeOfKnowledge #DigitalParenting #TikTokTruths #ChristConsciousness #AwakenedOnes #PeaceNotControl

