And speaking of lines—while I was on TikTok Live, I saw someone asking for a spell to force someone into confessing a crime. Made me stop and think… Doesn’t trying to force truth like that actually cancel out the truth itself? The act undermines the outcome. Truth can’t be manipulated into existence—it has to be lived.

