    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f510.svg"> 30/03/2025 - Thailand</strong>

This video isn’t about price, profit, or speculation.
It was recorded earlier in the year, using Bitcoin as a clear and practical example — because it makes the issue visible.

But the core message isn’t about Bitcoin itself; it’s about sovereignty and self-agency.

Bitcoin simply exposes a universal choice:
one path where you hold what’s yours,
and another where someone else does.

Most losses, scandals, and fear come from surrendering custody, outsourcing responsibility, and trusting intermediaries.

Financial sovereignty begins where dependency ends.

Self-custody isn’t advice — it’s a principle.
It’s about understanding, responsibility, and ownership, in any system.

This isn’t about timing markets.
It’s about preserving agency.

Not financial advice. Just a reflection on sovereignty, responsibility, and choice.

#FinancialSovereignty #Bitcoin #BTC #SelfCustody #SoundMoney #MonetaryFreedom #OwnYourKeys #Decentralization #InflationResistance #PersonalAgency #FinancialIndependence #FreedomThroughResponsibility #BitcoinEducation #SovereignIndividual

