This is a check-in about stepping back from heavy darkness, disengaging from what drains the spirit, and moving forward through quieter strength instead of endless exposure.
Sometimes the channels for change feel temporarily out of service… so the next best thing is to lead by example, protect your peace, and keep walking your own healing path.
