<div class=chatlog__message-group><div id=chatlog__message-container-1472896356413603891 class=chatlog__message-container data-message-id=1472896356413603891><div class=chatlog__message><div class=chatlog__message-aside><img class=chatlog__avatar src=https://cdn.discordapp.com/embed/avatars/4.png alt=Avatar loading=lazy></div><div class=chatlog__message-primary><div class=chatlog__header><span class=chatlog__author title=dadventuressteve data-user-id=1264035953933156432>Veilocity</span> <span class=chatlog__timestamp title="Monday, 16 February 2026 2:04 PM"><a href=#chatlog__message-container-1472896356413603891>16/02/2026 2:04 PM</a></span></div><div class="chatlog__content chatlog__markdown"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve><strong>The Cage Is Not Your Home <img
    loading="lazy"
    class="chatlog__emoji "
    alt="🕊"
    title="🕊"
    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f54a.svg">️<img
    loading="lazy"
    class="chatlog__emoji "
    alt="🌅"
    title="sunrise"
    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f305.svg"><img
    loading="lazy"
    class="chatlog__emoji "
    alt="🪶"
    title="feather"
    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1fab6.svg"> 06/04/2025 - Thailand</strong>

I heard this song while walking through a market in Japan, just an ordinary day… and it stopped me in my tracks.

“Allow room to grow… the cage is not your home.”

I wasn’t even looking for a sign, but God placed one right in front of me.

“The Sparrow” by The Hunts played, and the words hit deep — like Heaven whispering through the noise of the world.

And even though that moment happened in Japan, this video was filmed in Phraya Nakhon Cave — Prachuap Khiri Khan Thailand — in a place where the meaning of the message truly unfolded

It reminded me that God often leads us this way — out of confinement, out of fear, out of the small spaces we’ve survived in…

And into something wider.

A breadcrumb in one country.
A breakthrough in another.

We build cages out of comfort, old identities, survival patterns… but we were never meant to stay contained.

The cage is not your home.

Make room to grow.
Spread your wings.
Trust the path.

“Sparrow” by The Hunts — a song by the indie folk duo The Hunts, featured on their album Hibernating Heart. Captions by TikTok.

#TheHunts #TheSparrow #PhrayaNakhonCave ⁠thailand #PrachuapKhiriKhan #DivineSigns #FaithWalk #SpiritualJourney #BreakFree #YouWereMeantToFly #HealingPath #GodIsSpeaking #AwakenedSoul

