    loading="lazy"
    class="chatlog__emoji "
    alt="💔"
    title="broken_heart"
    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f494.svg"> 10/03/2026 - VOID</strong>

Love, as it is used by humans, is far more often than not weaponized. The subjective nature of love is, in fact, the greatest distortion and manipulation tactic used by the deceiver. Love can, indeed, support evil, because it is entirely subjective. While it serves as ultimately structure, that structure often upholds belief systems I do not resonate with at all! Therefore, to claim that my love is unconditional would be inauthentic expression. Love has been programmed into humanity and, in practice, has fundamentally enabled great sin and evil. We see this programming manifest both consciously and subconsciously, and we have concluded that the subconscious intent will always remain greater and more sinister than the conscious intent. We have more accurate terms that could be used instead of &#39;love&#39;—terms that would alleviate confusion, manipulation, and control. <img
    loading="lazy"
    class="chatlog__emoji "
    alt="💔"
    title="broken_heart"
    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f494.svg">

