    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f3ad.svg"> 13/08/2025 - Albania</strong>

Since April 2025, I’ve crossed 14 borders — not for adventure, but to stay ahead of a system that hunts me and my collective beyond every line on the map.
On 13 Sept 2024, final property orders were sealed in the NSW Family Court. Nearly a year later, when I felt safe, I bought my new home — a campervan. But Spirit had already told me: they’re coming.
...and now I carry the evidence. Proof that my connection to Spirit, to God-Source, is real… and that the system itself is a lie. The truth? The so-called “end times” prophecy of one-world government already happened... Clearly. Borders are theatre. Governments are branches of the same tree.
Do not consent.
Stop giving them your power.
Reclaim your sovereignty.

#TruthToLight #SystemicCorruption #NoBordersForJustice #GrandIllusion #OneWorldGovernment #BordersAreTheatre #EndTimesTruth #SpiritualAwakening #GodSource #DoNotConsent #WakeUp #MassAwakening #GovernmentCorruption #HiddenTruth #NewWorldOrder

