Politics isn’t always earned — it’s often purchased.
This isn’t said in anger, but in clarity.

Real change doesn’t require violent eruption. History shows a quieter path: spiritual resolve, fasting, persistence, and choosing truth over comfort.

Every time you rely more on God and less on the dollar, its control weakens.

The dollar reign ends the day we stop kneeling to it.

Withdraw your obedience — and the empire collapses under its own weight.

#IllusionOfDemocracy #DollarIsMaster #FastingForFreedom #FaithOverFear #LeanOnGod #SpiritualFreedom #BreakTheVeil #TruthOverTyranny #NewWaysOfLiving #ResistTheDollar

