I saw someone say yesterday that “nobody wants to see posts portraying victimhood.”
And sure, those posts might not get as many likes.
But if you’re posting so that there’s a witness—and as an effort to protect yourself from harm—then I say go for it.

I’m doing the same myself. ✌️ toodles!~

#SpeakYourTruth #StaySafe #YourVoiceMatters #Witness #HealingJourney #MentalHealthAwareness #SelfProtection #StandStrong #NoShame #KeepGoing

