    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f33f.svg"> 06/06/2025 - Bulgaria</strong>

...And in that loss, I gained something I never expected:
Clarity.
Society teaches us to layer up — titles, roles, identities — as if protection makes us stronger. But God showed me the truth: those layers were slowing me down.
The world says &quot;armor up.&quot; Heaven says, &quot;strip down to the soul.&quot;
In this video, I reflect on how the shedding of labels, roles, and even relationships has freed me. What I thought was weakness… turned out to be my greatest strength.
I move lighter now. I move faster. I move with God.

#SpiritualAwakening #LetGoToGrow #GodsStrength #IdentityInChrist #SoulFreedom #LiveUnburdened

