<div class=chatlog__message-group><div id=chatlog__message-container-1486972405254459422 class=chatlog__message-container data-message-id=1486972405254459422><div class=chatlog__message><div class=chatlog__message-aside><img class=chatlog__avatar src=https://cdn.discordapp.com/embed/avatars/4.png alt=Avatar loading=lazy></div><div class=chatlog__message-primary><div class=chatlog__header><span class=chatlog__author title=dadventuressteve data-user-id=1264035953933156432>Veilocity</span> <span class=chatlog__timestamp title="Friday, 27 March 2026 10:17 AM"><a href=#chatlog__message-container-1486972405254459422>27/03/2026 10:17 AM</a></span></div><div class="chatlog__content chatlog__markdown"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve><strong><img
